I think SoundWave has been used as spare pieces by Scattershot. The insane 
Alliance member now has a new jacket, I think.

::Dark One::

Dark One enters the CR room, stopping near one of the chambers, a bit aside 
from the others. "You may use this one. I need to get back to the battle."

He points at the CR, waiting for Squizzy to get in.
